translations: 大型垃圾装卸卡车；垃圾大铁桶

sentences.sentence: A large, green Dumpster. A couple of the maintenance folks.
sentences.translation: 一个大的，绿色的垃圾桶；几个公路维护人员，我看见很多沥青。

sentences.sentence: Put your head down in front of this garage. Under that dumpster is a big pile of money.
sentences.translation: 你低头看车库前面，在那个垃圾桶下面有一大撂钞票。

sentences.sentence: Jack Bauer had slipped to the back of the tavern and used a metal Dumpster to get a boost to the flat tar roof.
sentences.translation: 杰克·鲍尔悄悄走到酒馆后面，踩着一个金属大垃圾箱爬上铺着沥青的平坦屋顶。
